title: Did He Just Ruin His Relationship With This Proposal Prank?
description:
He tried to surprise his girlfriend with a proposal, but everything went wrong! His goal was to get her back to their house ASAP. So he told her that something was wrong with her dog.
Of course she rushed home, but she wasn't happy when she arrived. So what can he do to fix his mistake?
